description: For over 25 years, Barts Carts have put heart into the art of supplying parties across LA with fantastic food and service. With an arsenal of carnivalesque carts (BBQ, Caramel Apples, Churros, Funnel Cakes, Hot Dogs, Ice Cream, Cotton Candy, Tacos, Pretzels, and more!) at the ready, Barts Carts has a head start on catering to your culinary needs of all kinds. Plan your next party the smart way and reserve Barts Carts today!
name: Barts Carts
